The derelict supporters of Hamas claim to have established an Islamist month around Israel, from Lebanon in the north, led by the Hezbollah paramilitary group, to Syria, where the increasingly extremist rebels are about to overthrow the authority of Bashar Assad, and further to Jordan, where the King's authorities are threatened by Hamas's allies.
