At the same time, the strong-line supporters in Israel will come to the opposite conclusions.
In a military sense, Hamas was defeated.
The Israeli iron dome missile system has justified the cost of its establishment and successfully destroyed many of Hamas's missiles.
Israeli citizens can sleep in peace, at least for a while.
With regard to diplomacy, the US remained committed to its position; many European countries also blamed Hamas for the start of the last round of violence.
